note o  commitments and other
(1) lease commitments  the headquarters for the company is located at 220 south orange ave, livingston, new jersey. the company leases approximately 6,300 square feet of office space at 220 south orange avenue in livingston,
new jersey. the lease term expires june30, 2014 at a monthly cost of $6,942 which milestone believes to be competitive. the leased office space is in good condition. additionally, milestone leased a corporate apartment in maplewood, nj. this
lease expired in november 2010 at a monthly cost of $4,000. the company terminated the lease in december 2011. a third party distribution and logistics center in pennsylvania handles shipping and order fulfillment on a month-to-month basis.
milestone also leases office and telecom equipment under operating leases with payments ranging from $130-$522 per month.  aggregate minimum
rental commitments under noncancelable operating leases are as follows:
september 30,
$
83,828
